    <body>
      <section eId="sec_3324">
        <num>3324</num>
        <heading>Licenses to engage in research, instructional activities, and chemical analysis relating to controlled substances</heading>
        <subsection eId="sec_3324__subsec_a">
          <num>(a)</num>
          <content>
            <p>the name and address of the licensee;\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="sec_3324__subsec_b">
          <num>(b)</num>
          <content>
            <p>the nature of the project or projects permitted by the license;\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="sec_3324__subsec_c">
          <num>(c)</num>
          <content>
            <p>the nature of the controlled substance or substances to be used in\nthe project, by name if in schedule I, and by name or schedule or both\nif in any other schedule;\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="sec_3324__subsec_d">
          <num>(d)</num>
          <content>
            <p>whether dispensing to human subjects is permitted by the license.\n  5. Upon application of a person licensed pursuant to this title, a\nlicense may be amended to add a further activity or to add further\nsubstances or schedules to the project permitted thereunder. The fee for\nsuch amendment shall be twenty dollars.\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
      </section>
